quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,43,"Dájúdájú Àwa, Àwa l’À ń sọ ẹ̀dá di alààyè. A sì ń sọ ọ́ di òkú. Ọ̀dọ̀ Wa sì ni àbọ̀ ẹ̀dá."
  50,44,"(Rántí) ọjọ́ tí ilẹ̀ yóò fàya pẹ́rẹpẹ̀rẹ mọ́ wọn lára, (tí wọn yóò máa) yára (jáde láti inú ilẹ̀). Ìyẹn ni àkójọ tó rọrùn fún Wa."
  50,45,"Àwa nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń wí. Ìwọ kò sì níí jẹ wọ́n nípá (láti gbàgbọ́). Nítorí náà, fi al-Ƙur’ān ṣe ìrántí fún ẹni tí ó ń páyà ìlérí Mi."
  51,37,"A sì fi àmì kan sílẹ̀ nínú (ìlú náà) fún àwọn tó ń páyà ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro."
  51,38,"(Àmì tún wà) lára (Ànábì) Mūsā. Nígbà tí A fi ẹ̀rí pọ́nńbélé rán an níṣẹ́ sí Fir‘aon."
  51,39,"Ṣùgbọ́n ó lo gbogbo agbára rẹ̀ láti kẹ̀yìn sí òdodo. Ó sì wí pé: “Òpìdán tàbí wèrè kan (nìyí).”"
  52,28,"Dájúdájú àwa máa ń pè É tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Olóore, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.”"
  52,29,"Nítorí náà, ṣèrántí. Ìwọ kì í ṣe adábigba tàbí wèrè lórí ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa rẹ."
  52,30,"Tàbí wọ́n ń wí pé: “Eléwì kan tí à ń retí àpadàsí aburú fún ni.”"
  53,22,"Ìpín àbòsí nìyẹn nígbà náà."
  53,23,"(Àwọn orúkọ òrìṣà wọ̀nyẹn) kò sì jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe àwọn orúkọ kan tí ẹ̀yin àti àwọn bàbá yín sọ (àwọn òrìṣà yín fúnra yín). Allāhu kò sọ ẹ̀rí ọ̀rọ̀ kan kalẹ̀ nípa rẹ̀. Wọn kò sì tẹ̀lé kiní kan bí kò ṣe àbá dídá àti ohun tí ẹ̀mí (wọn) ń fẹ́ (ìfẹ́-inú). Ìmọ̀nà kúkú ti dé bá wọn láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wọn."
  53,24,"Tàbí ti ènìyàn ni n̄ǹkan tó bá ń fẹ́!"
  54,13,"A sì gbé (Ànábì) Nūh gun ọkọ̀ onípákó, ọkọ̀ eléṣòó,"
  54,14,"tí ó ń rìn (lórí omi) lójú Wa. (Ó jẹ́) ẹ̀san nítorí ẹni tí wọ́n ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú rẹ̀."
  54,15,"Dájúdájú A ṣẹ́ ẹ kù (tí A fi ṣe) àmì. Ǹjẹ́ olùrántí wà báyìí bí?"
  55,7,"Àti sánmọ̀, Allāhu gbé e sókè. Ó sì fi òṣùwọ̀n òfin déédé lélẹ̀ (fún ẹ̀dá)"
  55,8,"pé kí ẹ má ṣe tayọ ẹnu-ààlà níbi òṣùwọ̀n."
  55,9,"Ẹ gbé òṣùwọ̀n náà dúró pẹ̀lú dọ́gbadọ́gba. Kí ẹ sì má ṣe dín òṣùwọ̀n kù."